| 11  | 2    | 2          | 5       | 42            | +1 daily                       |
| 12  | 2    | 2          | 6       | 48            | +1 daily                       |
| 13  | 2    | 2          | 7       | 55            | +1 daily, 13th day done âœ…      |

âœ… **Final Total = 55**

